{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534423164&di=de89ef2192c8d4f74efccf0744ad3814&src=http%3A%2F%2Ff.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Fa5c27d1ed21b0ef436523272d5c451da81cb3e67.jpg","summary":"河北民族师范学院坐落在历史文化名城——承德市，其前身是始建于1907年经光绪皇帝御批设立的热河速成法政学堂，隶属学部。期间几经易名，1992年经原国家教委批准改办为承德民族师范高等专科学校。2010年3月，经教育部批准升格更名为河北民族师范学院，是河北省唯一一所民族本科高校，是河北省人民政府与国家民委共建地方高校。截至2016年8月，学校占地976.5亩，建筑面积27万平方米，教学仪器设备总值8000余万元，各类实验、实训室180个，纸质图书102万册，数字图书320万册。下设17个二级学院，有本科专业34个，专科专业40个，涵盖文学、理学、法学、工学、管理学、教育学、历史学、艺术学八大学科门类。有教职工815人，其中专任教师609人，教授63人，副教授190人。","tags":["师范类","本科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1907","所在地区":"河北省承德市桃李街26号","院校隶属":"河北省"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534423164&di=21b67340620b70ebdd792cf7597f0e91&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3771350272%2C901577040%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534423164&di=55116d9171fb2b8b17ebaa4e479c5046&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3633265429%2C770853797%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534423164&di=351701531252717440e3cb15de4ced8c&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D1411136079%2C2023392106%26fm%3D179%26app%3D42%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D300%26h%3D300","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534423164&di=125d59c15ed0d2f234a874650224dc13&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3700480986%2C838532854%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534423164&di=c00737c5ecbfdebd6a3ba24758a21952&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3661390211%2C894689707%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa